{2000}{}{These taxes are killing me.@@Band of socialist idiots.@@I want a smoke so badly.@@Fucking bureaucrats.@@One more directive and I'm going to kill somebody.@@I have to give them 90% of my income!@@This city is just insane.@@I'd gladly pay for that all, just leave me and my money alone.@@I'm gonna emigrate to Gecko, radiation be damned.}
{3000}{}{[He looks at you with his bright eyes.] Yes, @sex@|sir||ma'am|?@@What is that again?@@I'm listening, @sex@|sir||ma'am|.@@[Stares at you in silence.]@@[Pretends not to see you.]@@How can I help you?}
{3010}{}{Councillor McClure sent me to talk to you.}
{3020}{}{Why are you so upset?}
{3030}{}{How are you doing?}
{3040}{}{I'm a journalist, writing an article about Vault City. Would you mind if I asked you a couple of questions, sir?}
{3050}{}{Beautiful day, ain't it?}
{3060}{}{Well, nevermind.}
{4000}{}{Tell that fucking robber that if he'd like to talk to me, he'd better move his ass from his fancy office funded from my taxes.}
{5000}{}{Not your business, @sex@|fellow||darling|.}
{6000}{}{I'd feel better if you'd go away and stop wasting my time.}
{7000}{}{Excuse me, but I'm not talking with the press.}
{8000}{}{I wouldn't say so, @sex@|sir||ma'am|.}
{8010}{}{What's the problem, pal?}
{8020}{}{It's because that fucking Council, eh?}
{8030}{}{McClure sent me here.}
{8040}{}{[Remain silent.]}
{8050}{}{[Leave.]}
{9000}{}{Don't even tell me about those stupid fuckers.}
{10000}{}{What's your problem, @sex@|sir||ma'am|?}
{10010}{}{Just lookin' around. My name's @pname@, this is my first visit here. What can you tell me about this city?}
{10020}{}{Well, nevermind.}
{11000}{}{It's slowly rotting and will die soon because of those idiots in the Council.}
{11010}{}{What do you mean by that?}
{12000}{}{Just have a look at this. This city is almost dead. We don't produce anything, everything is being imported. Well, who'd bother producing anything, if he'd have to pay a 90% tax rate? If we weren't stocked with medical supplies for sale, we would've been bankrupt years ago.}
{12010}{}{Come on, if I was stocked with those supplies and didn't have to do anything, I'd be fucking happy!}
{12020}{}{That's interesting. Why people don't react?}
{12030}{}{Those fucking merchants aren't doing no good to anyone, they should pay 100% in taxes even.}
{12040}{}{I'll talk with McClure about this, he'll understand that.}
{13000}{}{Most Citizens are stupid as fuck, 'cause the teaching standards are incredibly low. All the books have been transcribed into electronic format, you can ask Kohl. That sounds nice, don't it? But the access to them is strictly limited! It isn't that necessary, to be honest, 'cause kids get brainwashed in the schools and people don't ever seek any information about the outside world.}
{13010}{}{If they are happy, what's the problem?}
{13020}{}{Man, I think it's good that you've got everything in one computer rather than on mountains of useless paper.}
{13030}{}{Councillor McClure won't like what you're saying.}
{13040}{}{But you have to admit that it's quite clean and safe here, compared to the rest of the wasteland.}
{14000}{}{I'm sorry, but I won't continue the conversation with someone with such a slave mentality. You would fit in well in San Francisco, fucking commie.}
{15000}{}{You seem to be too blunt to understand what I'm saying, sorry. Goodbye.}
{16000}{}{You're a Council spy?! Go away, scoundrel!}
{17000}{}{Yeah, sure - but remember, we had a fully equipped Vault and a G.E.C.K. to start with, and the rest had only burnt ashes of what remained after nuclear warfare. Look at what they achieved in Hub, Shady Sands, even Gecko. Just with the harsh, but simple rules of the wasteland like freedom, hard work and entrepreneurship. If we would only follow these rules, Vault City could become the greatest place in the world, a true oasis in the wasteland.}
{17010}{}{Maybe they've developed well, but safety is way more important than freedom.}
{17020}{}{How would you like to improve the state of your city?}
{17030}{}{You're an idiot, how can you compare this nice city with a shithole like Gecko!?}
{17040}{}{You should talk with Councillor McClure about it, he's a really nice man.}
{18000}{}{I would lower the taxes and let the private entrepreneurs do everything that is currently done by the state and funded with our money. Have you visited our pathetic "maintenance centers"? Even the shop in the outskirts of the city run by some poor slob in a shed is better supplied. Also, releasing servants and opening up for people of the outside would increase the amount of both consumers and workers, giving the economy a great boost.}
{18010}{}{If everything works fine operated by the state, why would you change it? People would just spoil it.}
{18020}{}{But you've got everything for free now, and you want people to pay. That's idiotic.}
{18030}{}{These are interesting ideas, I'll pass them to McClure when I talk with him again.}
{18040}{}{You know you won't change much by just standing and complaining here, Nigel.}
{19000}{}{[He looks quite depressed as he realizes that.]}
{19010}{}{How can I help you?}
{20000}{}{You seem to be reasonable @sex@|guy||girl|, @pname@. What do you suggest I should do?}
{20010}{}{You should keep your thoughts to yourself, Nigel. You're unable to change anything, and you will only bring the attention of those damn officials. Keep out of the trouble, that's my advice.}
{20020}{}{I think you should keep fighting, Nigel. Behind the mask of democracy and happiness, this city has become an autocratic regime. We have to change it before it's too late.}
{21000}{}{Yeah, I think you're right. It's been too long that the city's been run like this and Citizens are being told pure bullshit over and over again. I won't be bothering anybody no more.}
{21010}{}{Goodbye, Nigel.}
{22000}{}{Thank you, @pname@. You've heard what I've said. Go to Councillor McClure and repeat it to him. He seems to be the only clever guy in that fucking Council, maybe he could tell them something...}
{22010}{}{I'll do that. Goodbye, Nigel.}
{23000}{}{Go away, idiot.@@I don't want to talk with you.@@I've got nothing more to say.@@Begone.@@Leftist scum.}
{24000}{}{Thanks for your help.@@I hope it all will turn out well.@@You're really smart.@@I apparently needed to talk to someone like you.}

